'''Samana''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]], located on the southern tip of the [[Betu/Legends|Betu]] continent. Although it was possible to land in Samana, control officials highly suggested the legal [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] at [[Equator City/Legends|Equator City]] around [[3 ABY/Legends|3.5 ABY]].

[[Smuggler/Legends|Smugglers]] who defied [[Navik the Red|the Grand Protector]]'s forces and supplied the [[Chekkoo clan/Legends|Chekkoo clan]], sometimes opted to land in Samana and make their way to the [[Chekkoo Province]] by land.

